=== Internal Assessment Marks Management System ===

REQUIREMENTS:
  - Python 3.x
  - flask  (pip install flask)

  Note: flask-cors is NOT required anymore.

HOW TO RUN:
  1. Extract the zip to a folder, e.g. C:\co-po-updated-v2\
  2. Open PowerShell or Command Prompt in that folder
  3. Run:
       cd backend
       pip install -r ..\requirements.txt
       py app.py
  4. Open your browser and go to:
       http://localhost:5000

  DO NOT open the HTML files directly — always use the URL above.

