HOW IT WORKS:
  1. Login at http://localhost:5000
  2. My Courses page  ->  create one or more courses
  3. Select a course  ->  goes to Dashboard
  4. Setup            ->  set number of COs, internals, assignments
  5. Students         ->  add students for the course
  6. Marks Entry      ->  select internal, enter marks

NOTES:
  - Each course has its own students, setup, and marks.
  - Different courses do NOT share data.
  - CO checkboxes in setup are generated based on the number you enter.
